  <brief_title>Whole Body Vibration Exercise for Elderly With Cognitive Impairments</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Whole Body Vibration Exercise Training on Physical Functioning and Falls in Community-dwelling Elderly With Cognitive Impairments</official_title>
